Launching LSC WebAI
===================

For Linux or Mac users, go to this folder and launch the lsc-webai.sh startup script:

  cd $INSTALL_DIR
  ./lsc-webai.sh start

For Windows users, go to the install folder and double click on lsc-webai.bat.

To stop the application, call the lsc-webai.sh with the stop argument, under Linux or
Mac:

  cd $INSTALL_DIR
  ./lsc-webai.sh stop

For Windows users simply close the cmd panel.

Accessing to LSC WebAI
======================

When the Jetty server have started you can access LSC Web Administrative Interface using
a web explorer at http://localhost:8080/. 

! IMPORTANT SECURITY NOTICE !
=============================
!! Take care that all identifiers and passwords used to connect to data sources are stored
in a clear text format and are rendered through this administrative application. Please
consider block any unauthorized access through a firewall rule, a Jetty security
configuration or an HTTP authentifying reverse proxy in order to protect them.

